Description: Workflows loaded in parallel or sequence
Difference  in hour/minutes between Lu - End Date and Lu - Start Date
SELECT:
(
  CASE 
  WHEN (trunc(("ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."END_DT" - "ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."ST_DT")*24) <= 9)
  THEN '0'
  END
  )
 || trunc(("ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."END_DT" - "ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."ST_DT")*24) || 'h ' ||
   (
  CASE 
  WHEN (trunc(mod(("ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."END_DT" - "ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."ST_DT")*24,1)*60) <= 9)
  THEN '0'
  END
  ) 
  || trunc(mod(("ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."END_DT" - "ADM_TRT_ST_LU"."ST_DT")*24,1)*60) || 'm'
(@Select(Loading Unit\Dimensions\Lu - End Date) -@Select(Loading Unit\Dimensions\Lu - Start Date) )*1024
